				<wikidot:authorName>Doctor Cimmerian</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1414765</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>New Skip before the New Year. Been working on this for a couple days, trying to get it just right. There is an audio element that autoplays, but it's not a jump scare. Still, I really hope you read the warnings (and took them seriously). This uses html5, so it won't work on most (if any) mobile devices. Hope you like it.</p> <p>Special thanks to Decibelle, Reach, and Scantron for helping me flesh the story out a bit more.</p> 
				 	]]>
